Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
if GLOB_CONTEXT = 5 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 interior = 0 gs_path_move = 0 endif
call "VehiclePathMacro" parameters all A = A, wheelBase = wheelBase, wheelDiam = wheelDiam, hsId = 1000, gs_path_move = gs_path_move, gs_path_show_3D = gs_path_show_3D, gs_pathNodes_Num = gs_pathNodes_Num, gs_pathNodes_Num_old = gs_pathNodes_Num_old, gs_pathNodes_Pos = gs_pathNodes_Pos, gs_pathNodes_Angle = gs_pathNodes_Angle, gs_pathNodes_Speed = gs_pathNodes_Speed, gs_path_fps = gs_path_fps, gs_path_start_frame = gs_path_start_frame, gs_path_pen = gs_path_pen, gs_path_line_pen = gs_path_line_pen, returned_parameters wheelAngle, wheelRot, posX,posY,posZ, dirAngle, riseAngle
add posX,posY,posZ rotz dirAngle roty riseAngle
if gs_path_move then wheel_angle = wheelAngle endif
! ============================================================================= ! Draw the Car ! =============================================================================
rotz 180 addx -wheelBase
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
define material "builtInMatBlackTyre" 0, 0.1, 0.1, 0.1, 0.86, 0.81, 0.09, 0, 2.2, 0, 0.990005, 0.990005, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0
pen gs_cont_pen
roty -gs_rot_ver rotx gs_rot_hor
mulsize = 5.096/0.571
MUL mulsize ,mulsize ,mulsize ROTz -90 ADD 0,0.34,0.025
ADD 0.002875,-0.169,0 MATERIAL gs_carbody_mat call "cp_car05_body" parameters DEL 1
ADD 0,-0.23322,0 MATERIAL gs_carbody_mat call "cp_car05_basic" parameters DEL 1
ADD 0,0.05278,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_lamp_mat call "cp_car05_frontLamp" parameters DEL 1
ADD 0,0.05389,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_mirror_mat call "cp_car05_frontLamp_back" parameters DEL 1
IF wheel<0.5 THEN MUL -1,1,1 ADD -0.003613,-0.196744,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_glass_mat call "cp_car05_glass" parameters DEL 1 IF wheel<0.5 THEN DEL 1
ADD 0,-0.420206,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_blamp_mat call "cp_car05_rearLamp" parameters DEL 1
ADD -0.00017,0.0169,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_access_mat call "cp_car05_chrome" parameters DEL 1
ADD 0,-0.068578,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_mirror_mat call "cp_car05_extMirror" parameters DEL 1
ADD -0.00089,-0.21472,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_access_mat2 call "cp_car05_outaccess_01" parameters DEL 1
ADD 0,0.06227,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_access_mat2 call "cp_car05_outaccess_03" parameters DEL 1
IF interior then IF wheel<0.5 THEN MUL -1,1,1 ADD 0,-0.18985,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_int_mat1 call "cp_car05_carpet_01" parameters DEL 1 ADD -0.006805,-0.1141,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_int_mat1 call "cp_car05_carpet_02" parameters DEL 1 ADD -0.030695,-0.13652,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_int_mat1 call "cp_car05_carpet_03" parameters DEL 1 ADD 0,-0.12711,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_int_mat3 call "cp_car05_intChrome" parameters DEL 1 ADD -0.000185,-0.071595,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_mirror_mat call "cp_car05_intMirror" parameters DEL 1 ADD 0.00003,-0.134,0.0073 MATERIAL gs_int_mat1 call "cp_car05_intMirror_back" parameters DEL 1 IF wheel<0.5 THEN DEL 1
ADD -0.00006,-0.22604,0.00475 MATERIAL gs_int_mat2 call "cp_car05_seats" parameters DEL 1 ENDIF
DEL 3
wheelmul=0.72/0.64 add 0,-0.85,0 rotz -90 MUL wheelmul,wheelmul,wheelmul gosub 30 del 3
add 0,0.85,0 rotz 90 MUL wheelmul,wheelmul,wheelmul gosub 30 del 3
add wheelBase, -0.85,0 rotz -90+wheel_angle MUL wheelmul,wheelmul,wheelmul gosub 30 del 3
add wheelBase, 0.85, 0 rotz 90+wheel_angle MUL wheelmul,wheelmul,wheelmul gosub 30 del 3
DEL 1 !!DEL 3
END !!!!!!!!**************************************** !!!!!!!!**************************************** END !!!!!!!!****************************************

prism_ 2, 0.04, 0, 0, 979, 0.24, 360, 4079
for i = 1 to 5 cutend next i del 2
addx 0.0625 roty -90 cylind 0.08, 0.15 del 2 else resol 12 material "builtInMatBlackTyre" revolve 6, 360, 0, -0.12, 0.255, 1, -0.12, 0.30, 1, -0.10, 0.32, 1, 0.10, 0.32, 1, 0.12, 0.30, 1, 0.12, 0.255, 1
material gs_wheel_mat roty -90 addz -0.115 prism_ 4, 0.23, 0, 0, 979, 0.255, 360, 4079, 0, 0, 979, 0.24, 360, 4079 del 1 addz -0.105 prism_ 2, 0.22, 0, 0, 979, 0.24, 360, 4079 del 2 endif del 1 return
Symbol.Script_VL:
VALUES "A" 5.100 VALUES "B" 2.106 VALUES "ZZYZX" 1.500
LOCK "A","B","ZZYZX"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_rot_ver" range[-45,45] values "gs_rot_hor" range[-30,30]
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif
if not(interior) then lock "wheel" if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then lock "wheel", "interior", "gs_int_mat1", "gs_int_mat2", "gs_int_mat3" parameters interior=0 endif if not(interior) then lock "gs_int_mat1", "gs_int_mat2", "gs_int_mat3"
call "VehiclePathMacro" parameters A = A, gs_path_move = gs_path_move, gs_path_show_2D = gs_path_show_2D, gs_path_show_3D = gs_path_show_3D, gs_pathNodes_Num = gs_pathNodes_Num, gs_pathNodes_Num_old = gs_pathNodes_Num_old, gs_pathNodes_Pos = gs_pathNodes_Pos, gs_pathNodes_Angle = gs_pathNodes_Angle, gs_pathNodes_Speed = gs_pathNodes_Speed, gs_path_fps = gs_path_fps, gs_path_start_frame = gs_path_start_frame
